OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA chilly start once again, with
OL,6,Fearly frost, fog and low cloud soon
OL,7,Fclearing to leave another dry and
OL,8,Fsunny day. Warmer than Thursday with
OL,9,Flighter winds, but feeling cooler
OL,10,Ftowards the east coast where some low
OL,11,Fcloud could linger.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FStaying dry overnight.
OL,14,FTemperatures falling to again give a
OL,15,Frisk of rural frost, with low cloud,
OL,16,Fmist and fog patches once again for
OL,17,Fmany parts by dawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
