OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FAnother dry and fine day
OL,6,Fexpected once early low cloud, mist
OL,7,Fand fog clears. Sunshine through the
OL,8,Fafternoon but likely cloudier into the
OL,9,Fevening. Temperatures remaining warm.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FDry
OL,12,Fwith some hazy sunshine Sunday after
OL,13,Fany early low cloud clears, warm for
OL,14,Fmost. Monday sees a risk of some
OL,15,Fshowers. Drier again into Tuesday but
OL,16,Fturning breezier.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
